{"tid":803552,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"親戚問銀行借錢投資金礦","createTime":"2018-09-02T11:10:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T10:57:21.000Z","uid":24778,"like":3,"dislike":55,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"62c272b47241ad42eac751a0824e819c7bbf63b2","tid":803552,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"親戚問銀行借左一百萬，話投資金礦。<br />\n<br />\n佢話agent同佢講澳洲公司the victor smorgon group本身係有好多唔同的生意，但冇金礦的資產，所以想搵人合資開發金礦。如果開發得成，會每年派22%息，（100萬即係每年派22萬）會年年派。如果三年後開發唔到，會賠番5%就完。<br />\n<br />\n我上網做research搵間公司又係澳洲公司，而個老細peter edwards又真係首富，成件好似冇伏咁。但如果peter edwards真係咁有錢，佢使鬼搵你地班旦散一齊夾錢掘金咩？<br />\n<br />\n我唔識投資，又唔識金，所以想問下大家知唔知間公司，感謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/190346_86023fa2bdd09661a52cd00b96bf5150.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F190346_86023fa2bdd09661a52cd00b96bf5150.png&h=360d937e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99f0820a850d34a336ebe63f7544f06bae93158c","tid":803552,"uid":14606,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"我呢排都賺夠 想分d畀人"},{"pid":"cff2be3b2ea11bd6357d6d2b566428966d6dfb3a","tid":803552,"uid":24778,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"99f0820a850d34a336ebe63f7544f06bae93158c","tid":803552,"uid":14606,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"我呢排都賺夠 想分d畀人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:13:24.000Z","msg":"邊有咁好死 但我又冇証據証明係伏 點算？"},{"pid":"b15b4bc43cf66e009e3324746a1f2faee5ca9025","tid":803552,"uid":5686,"like":45,"dislike":0,"score":45,"quote":{"pid":"cff2be3b2ea11bd6357d6d2b566428966d6dfb3a","tid":803552,"uid":24778,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"99f0820a850d34a336ebe63f7544f06bae93158c","tid":803552,"uid":14606,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:12:41.000Z","msg":"我