,"tid":803552,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:36:52.000Z","msg":"龐氏_ _<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e200f9568b54c95f95a76db18cb549dfb103ecaa","tid":803552,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:38:24.000Z","msg":"未見過誠哥會出黎做生招牌"},{"pid":"e769f3a7276d950ff9b159266874b199ef111239","tid":803552,"uid":159454,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:02:43.000Z","msg":"佢只不過每年係個本金到派 22%比你<br />\n<br />\n到個本金派完剩番小小就同佢講掘唔到咩貴價礦<br />\n投資虧蝕 咁你d 錢就拎黎填晒佢d 債呀 期下工程公司支出呀 管理費呀咁樣"},{"pid":"b67104903ff5f8eddfa813861554744a6f0fb630","tid":803552,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f04b5c2fae0d3daa51bb0b1be9eec66fc538e1a","tid":803552,"uid":18955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:36:52.000Z","msg":"龐氏_ _<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:05:40.000Z","msg":"_ _ 騙 局 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdf596b68984cdbcd81fd8da06ae8f9c3f284ec","tid":803552,"uid":9942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:11:18.000Z","msg":"唔呃你班傻西點做首富"},{"pid":"9b45660f06607df67bfc79628c13baddfc6337df","tid":803552,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62c272b47241ad42eac751a0824e819c7bbf63b2","tid":803552,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-02T11:10:06.000Z","msg":"親戚問銀行借左一百萬，話投資金礦。<br />\n<br />\n佢話agent同佢講澳洲公司the victor smorgon group本身係有好多唔同的生意，但冇金礦的資產，所以想搵人合資開發金礦。如果開發得成，會每年派22%息，（100萬即係每年派22萬）會年年派。如果三年後開發唔到，會賠番5%就完。<br />\n<br />\n我上網做research搵間公司又係澳洲公司，而個老細peter edwards又真係首富，成件好似冇伏咁。但如果peter edwards真係咁有錢，佢使鬼搵你地班旦散一齊夾錢掘金咩？<br />\n<br />\n我唔識投資，又唔識金，所以想問下大家知唔知間公司，感謝！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/02/190346_86023fa2bdd09661a52cd00b96bf5150.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F02%2F190346_86023fa2bdd09661a52cd00b96bf5150.png&h=360d937e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"成班都文盲<br />\n<br />\n都唔好講佢成件事係唔係真， 當佢係， 都寫明<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果開發得成</span>，會每年派22%息，（100萬即係每年派22萬）會年年派。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果三年後開發唔到</span>，會賠番5%就完。<br />\n<br />\n個個就話每年派22%肯定呃人。 你買馬都有機會中10倍啦。 不過輸晒既機會更大咁解之嘛。"},{"pid":"1eeb464f7a1ebb1fe9039a3ecc2135f62a6642a0","tid":803552,"uid":198952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"22x3+5&lt;100"},{"pid":"caff347aae19629fb3ea8eeb03e50d0bad7b5154","tid":803552,"uid":39013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:45:05.000Z","msg":"唉屌 真係做老千好過<br />\n依家D人真係咁撚死豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb58e62d48b0f8ededebacb80f8979d1d5c563db","tid":803552,"uid":206087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:45:34.000Z","msg":"澳洲金 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1754c292c87ddd30045d3917e9893fe54da556d3","tid":803552,"uid":48526,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"係真都唔出奇, 因為做礦風險好高, 一個礦場好大, 但只能探幾個洞就決定去唔去開採, 同賭冇咩分別, 如果中左每年分22%俾人其實好少, 澳洲聽講有暴利稅, 做礦中左會要交得好勁下.<br />\n<br />\n所以風險你地食, 中左先分22%俾你, 其實好著數. <br />\n<br />\n我有朋友澳洲做礦, 我聽佢講."},{"pid":"1462123927aa1a9bcdb102b7fea47962b2783208","tid":803552,"uid":110486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T02:57:55.000Z","msg":"22%要你啲散紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22bd207e72