><br />\n其實有得解<br />\n同你講係香港沙頭角做同一樣野你一定唔信<br />\n但多數人對外國認識最多都只係做過遊客<br />\n根本唔清楚係點就易上釣好多<br />\n就算同你講炒的士牌你都好易搵到大約點做<br />\n但同你講做原始股東入股水幤網到上市有股份分一上就贏幾十倍（之前好似有單就係用原始股呃人）<br />\n正常人唔會知係乜又諗落一贏就發達<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:44:10.000Z","msg":"真心呃人要用外國人呃"},{"pid":"0315cf02f109aeea653152959ae2b1a6a54b759b","tid":803552,"uid":182325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:49:14.000Z","msg":"貪心既人就要比人懲罰，唔係唔識長進<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ef1256d559a83bac681156db83e5a7e6561fb1","tid":803552,"uid":85552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:56:49.000Z","msg":"搵幾個似樣既鬼佬，book間酒店影下相，成本都唔洗十萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n昆一個就一球嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8570a1dd18d25c02f512d3d3287bce87dba4e85","tid":803552,"uid":145923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"借一百萬應該係按樓,有樓唔怕啦.樓價升咁多.比人呃番D當做回吐."},{"pid":"f6f4ac29f14547c5f805c34c4ce36901cf9ad19e","tid":803552,"uid":7123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:09:28.000Z","msg":"如果開發得成，會每年派22%息，（100萬即係每年派22萬）會年年派。如果三年後開發唔到，會賠番5%就完。<br />\n<br />\n老奉都開發唔到 食你95萬"},{"pid":"32df1399da5d696f6f569ff346bcea92a9576d37","tid":803552,"uid":205455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"122cce37e37fb93911390aeba4145c8e9b813976","tid":803552,"uid":24778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22bd207e725ba88969e24a66071e9f1f2860d0cc","tid":803552,"uid":89225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:00:12.000Z","msg":"勸唔掂。不如你話你開銀礦40%回報叫佢投資下"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"我放棄啦 佢咁大個人（成50歲）我真係幫佢唔到～"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T05:09:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cde154f0f8